{"type": "article", "id": 49299, "title": "拿植物标本作装饰，现在不需要自己亲自动手了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-16T23:19:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47117, "name": "装饰画"}, {"id": 1672, "name": "沙发"}, {"id": 47118, "name": "收纳柜"}, {"id": 2319, "name": "咖啡杯"}, {"id": 2263, "name": "台灯"}, {"id": 47119, "name": "暖水袋"}, {"id": 47120, "name": "IMONS"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 47121, "name": "Studio Inma Bermúdez"}, {"id": 32686, "name": "熹山工房"}, {"id": 8331, "name": "吱音"}, {"id": 47122, "name": "暖澡堂自然研究所"}, {"id": 47123, "name": "Noé Duchaufour Lawrance"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 137, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180116224644d4RavA3zD8HwLPxu.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>立体植物标本画 by 暖澡堂自然研究所 ZAO Nature Lab</h3><p>暖澡堂自然研究所（ZAO Nature Lab）成立于 2016 年初，是一个专注自然美学创造的独立品牌。这些立体植物标本画选择了由植物，香料和种子制成。大家谈到植物，大部分时候只关注到它的花和叶子，但其实植物的种子与果实形态经常会超出你想象。而这次的立体标本画，就是想要将这种奇妙的美感带入到人们眼前，甚至生活中。</p><p>因为植物标本本身比较具象，而且细节与质感丰富，所以设计上尽量弱化框子的存在感，去掉边框，全部以透明亚克力这种比较现代感的材料替代，让整体看上去更加纯粹而精致。同时，设计师在侧面进行封边，尽量阻绝标本与空气的接触。以及侧边的透明设计也能从侧面看到立体标本的形态。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224717TH85Z0aEpPqWBYAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224718NbWfGM0ixEQh6gOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224719GEdT32qvHJtbrZeu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224720kPp1avD70rBhxyC3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801162247215WopBOmduw9iTr1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224722aBe7CdQkriGVvzRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>暖水袋捂手枕 by 吱音</h3><p>原创家居设计品牌吱音最近升级了其经典款暖水袋抱枕，同时实现了布料与设计上的升级，荷兰丝绒布料以及双边的开口，优雅也温暖。立体的暖水袋捂手枕具有高度抓牢力的枕芯，撑起了具有光泽阴影的荷兰丝绒。</p><p>双边的开口，让暖水袋造型的抱枕成了暖“手”袋。双手可以放在里面取暖，适当的高度与蓬松感，刚好能让头舒适的枕于其上，亦是办公室里短暂午睡的温暖小物，枕内芯的棉絮具有高度的抓牢力与回弹力。售价 99 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c-s.w5003-17549343977.1.1f2324112t4s47&amp;id=563282232214&amp;scene=taobao_shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224756VRdOxXJKZk8mIhgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224757FkQw0blJje1DsE63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224757F3Cr82SAjPJQKV5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224757uQ6ktrqm9PfAw1px.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224758YMpmUc2n50wPIZS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224758P4BuFzZijIad09DE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.640000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>丘田组合柜 by 熹山工房</h3><p>自由百变，不拘一格，是这款丘田组合柜的最大特点，它可以满足你各种收纳需求，竖格柜可用作书架，三格柜可用作器物展示，复古手工制的水波纹玻璃柜可收纳酒杯、茶具等，纯铜铸造拉手的抽屉柜可收纳一些较为私密的小物件，它们可以自由组合用于书房、餐厅、卧室以及客厅等空间，分为樱桃木、榉木和胡桃木三种材质，售价 320 至 2200 元不等，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.1-c-s.w5003-15741634106.3.128ddfe7r4jUjU&amp;id=560686851733&amp;scene=taobao_shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224831ZBpeUmz7DS0hVI8l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801162248319Xsh68fwF2GkrB1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.910667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801162248335fXbrgwAduHY4CLI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.104000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224834HRnxLYgaU54qVyMr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.908000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Olivia Table Lamp by Studio Inma Bermúdez</h3><p>西班牙设计工作室 Studio Inma Bermúdez 为家居设计品牌造作设计了这款橄榄台灯。设计师从可爱呆萌的橄榄中获得灵感，设计了这款台灯，有着浑圆的橄榄外形。灯头由大小灯罩通过永久磁铁连接，大灯罩可以 260°球面旋转，自由调整角度，增大照明区域，点亮任意空间，满足你不同照明需求。</p><p>灯泡选用色温 3000K 的中性光源，自然柔和不刺眼。雾面灯泡让光更好的折射发散，减少直射，降低对眼睛的伤害，更适读写与办公。橄榄台灯分为圆球款和圆柱款，售价 299 元，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300247\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224908im1IbZqNtxlGVCgX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560185\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224908MATEeqJl3c4pbkwQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224908TaPR8M2bxmXIYJp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224909lwNtdMPWEn9ZJecq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Belle Ile Sofa by Noé Duchaufour Lawrance</h3><p>这款名为贝岛的沙发，出自法国设计师 Noé Duchaufour Lawrance 之手。沙发蜿蜒轮廓的灵感，源自深入大西洋半岛的海岸线形态，没有一根垂直线条的设计语言。从扶手角到沙发全框架，通体圆润，不见一个尖锐棱角。</p><p>沙发背面、侧面均圆润打造，弧面落地设计，任何细微角度都不见垂直线。沙发内框架以贝壳张开的瞬间形态为灵感打造，面料提取法国布列塔尼的香草紫、米杏两种标志性色，80% 涤纶加 20%麻混纺而成，获得透气不燥、经久耐用的质感。售价 4999 元起，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300236\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224948xnB37LGruq6vS42O.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562222\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224948ZuaT8UIKy7hgm3p0.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224948480wBnYuj6dfozaZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116224951fOZ3rlSsh4nDwLHm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>妙思咖啡杯 CP001 by IMONS</h3><p>这是一款随身自动咖啡机，适用日本 UCC 咖啡胶囊、咖啡粉、茶等原料来制作新鲜饮品，机器内置充电池，倒入热水，按下电源键 5 秒，红灯亮起，机器开始制作热饮。或是倒入冷水，街上电源或是车载电源，按下电源键 2 秒，机器工作烧水并制作热饮。600mAh 容量的锂电池，充电一小时可以使用约 100 次。售价 799 元，<a href=\"http://imons-cafe.com/ProductDetail/1392826.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116225031W7oHVL8249GZFvRk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751584\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116225032ja10zDwF8lrEYKdR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.602532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116225032C4I9s7T38i0Fq6yt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.862770\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116225032fDutw0ZaW2M4k8bl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749367\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180116225035hOkL7CEjwIStlGmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749367\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}